00:22:20,547 --> 00:22:22,090
This?

275
00:22:23,008 --> 00:22:25,010
It's pretty. Did you find it here?

276
00:22:26,011 --> 00:22:27,137
Yes,

277
00:22:27,304 --> 00:22:30,015
